          <protein>
            <id type="integer">5154</id>
            <name>Growth factor receptor-bound protein 2</name>
            <uniprot-id>P62993</uniprot-id>
            <description>Isoform GRB3-3 does not bind to phosphorylated epidermal growth factor receptor (EGFR) but inhibits EGF-induced transactivation of a RAS-responsive element. Isoform GRB3-3 acts as a dominant negative protein over GRB2 and by suppressing proliferative signals, may trigger active programmed cell death</description>
